-21T16:45:07.000Z","msg":"試過俾個OL用屎忽不停磨我條丁<br />\n初頭見佢彎腰攞野時個屎忽磨到我，就以為佢唔小心<br />\n但攞完又攞，攞左好多次都磨到我<br />\n利申：183cm高"},{"pid":"6fe373cb3ba2762ae6534090ea8a93a1ed5c9fa3","tid":165420,"uid":77871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:47:51.000Z","msg":"另外試過有一次條女成對波迫埋黎迫左幾個站"},{"pid":"32a028eb5fcd9b29db058394f729b80c1c598cf1","tid":165420,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T17:28:23.000Z","msg":"仲要係佢身邊係咁索香水味<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b576a6608f68b3df99e2ee4820dc5f9733fc0284","tid":165420,"uid":45872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T17:29:43.000Z","msg":"有次迫鐵隔離女女着熱褲 feel到大家啲腳毛不斷互相糾纏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdb0afe0c373089019a7da5634600f698b05196","tid":165420,"uid":33050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:16:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上面條女<br />\n睇相就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇片即刻鳩縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫王緒緒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=onw6vTezctI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Donw6vTezctI&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm926tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=574174f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=onw6vTezctI</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d369cbd5f843f38ef51d77f52f5ebd607357d9fd","tid":165420,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT